Security architecture
------------------------------
-replay - is where copy of a legitimate messagee is captured and retransmitted later.
         -involves interception and delay.
         -it is an attack on intergrity because it is not send on timely manner .
         -the connection message is lagitmate.
 -Denial of service attacks - intruder  preventing the two communication parties from 
                             communicating or accessing the communication channel.
                             -it is availability attack because the is a timelineness factor.
                             - Intruder is stopping all messages from reaching the destination.

























